nodes.text: Padawans, Pirates and Princesses—A Chronological Guide

Padawans, Pirates and Princesses — A Chronological Guide was a Studio Fun International Star Wars reference title targeted at young audiences in grades 1-6. It was to be released on September 19, 2017, at 128 pages long.

Discover details in the exciting lives of all the women from the Star Wars universe! Fold-out flaps and more create an interactive experience as fans learn all about Rey, Princess Leia, Maz Kanata, Padmé Amidala, Captain Phasma, and other fan favorites!
